pression <br />\n食緊venlafaxine lyrica"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T14:43:18.000Z","msg":"KEEP住食,唔停藥既話有冇副作用?<br />\n有冇影響學業/工作?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T22:44:59.000Z","msg":"Sorry 巴打睇唔到你reply<br />\n停藥副作用大啲<br />\n依家係零記性，其他可能慣咗就還好<br />\n影響工作一定有，冇記性，專注力差咗"},{"pid":"7e3fefb0ba1dd783ed043aab89fddc84d51700c0","tid":1074112,"uid":125903,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a2da912eb03231b6ddc06c72f46eac83e03be62b","tid":1074112,"uid":179374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2aa01efa644c7dde6d73eeac2320e337aafd995a","tid":1074112,"uid":125903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca461b621dbedda08918fc8ba9121d8109e26688","tid":1074112,"uid":179374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-23T08:13:23.000Z","msg":"Depression <br />\n食緊venlafaxine lyrica"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T14:43:18.000Z","msg":"KEEP住食,唔停藥既話有冇副作用?<br />\n有冇影響學業/工作?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T22:44:59.000Z","msg":"Sorry 巴打睇唔到你reply<br />\n停藥副作用大啲<br />\n依家係零記性，其他可能慣咗就還好<br />\n影響工作一定有，冇記性，專注力差咗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T08:59:55.000Z","msg":"唔緊要, 我自己覆得遲啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都係冇記性同專注力差, 做唔夠一粒鐘野就想離開一陣個種<br />\n加油呀巴打, 努力克服個病~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24966ed7b21a036fe03b86cc52db0118e30159e0","tid":1074112,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T09:47:41.000Z","msg":"食左10年抗憶屈,醫生唔比停.........."},{"pid":"e8e8171b24c61df3eda99999f24d6cfea5bec74c","tid":1074112,"uid":105102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T09:56:52.000Z","msg":"唔好自己停藥，會好大鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1650ae841561859c94caf4199648e76a5050f507","tid":1074112,"uid":209263,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T10:27:02.000Z","msg":"四年前 抑鬱加焦慮<br />\n食咗一年半血清素同安眠藥<br />\n會依賴咗藥物<br />\n一唔開心就叫醫生開鎮靜劑俾我<br />\n<br />\n食咗年幾<br />\n其實覺得自己戒唔到<br />\n但見到屋企人好擔心我<br />\n所以就好決斷咁戒咗<br />\n<br />\n其實呢兩年都會好唔開心<br />\n甚至比有病嘅時候 更加抑鬱<br />\n但宜家會知道係唔可以靠藥<br />\n一定要靠自己搵到一個方法去令自己開心啲<br />\n<br />\n我跑咗半年步<br />\n每次出完汗 都覺得開心咗"},{"pid":"1096c3f7a031b1a1f4e9b44fdf6f7c3dc3d4abaf","tid":1074112,"uid":125903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24966ed7b21a036fe03b86cc52db0118e30159e0","tid":1074112,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T09:47:41.000Z","msg":"食左10年抗憶屈,醫生唔比停.........."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T14:56:30.000Z","msg":"我估自己已經有十年,但實際食藥都係呢幾年<br />\n加油呀巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw我成日有留意你d post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80ff7d333840023106d18f9d50994ae11352c168","tid":1074112,"uid":125903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8e8171b24c61df3eda99999f24d6cfea5bec74c","tid":1074112,"uid":105102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T09:56:52.000Z","msg":"唔好自己停藥，會好大鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T14:56:49.000Z","msg":"巴打有經驗?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b36db7e0af0772617313749d960b76231e5faaaf","tid":1074112,"uid":125903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1650ae841561859c94caf4199648e76a5050f507","tid":1074112,"uid":209263,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T10:27:02.000Z","msg":"四年前 抑鬱加焦慮<br />\n食咗一年半血清素同安眠藥<br />\n會依賴咗藥物<br />\n一唔開心就叫醫生開鎮靜劑俾我<br />\n<br />\n食咗年幾<br />\n其實覺得自己戒唔到<br />\n但見到屋企人好擔心我<br />\n所以就好決斷咁戒咗<br />\n<br />\n其實呢兩年都會好唔開心<br />\n甚至比有病嘅時候 更加抑鬱<br />\n但宜家會知道係唔可以靠藥<br />\n一定要靠自己搵到一個方法去令自己開心啲<br />\n<br />\n我跑咗半年步<br />\n每次出完汗 都覺得開心咗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T14:57:49.000Z","msg":"而家無食藥兼好返哂?"},{"pid":"bcc0eb94aaad366824f5af3fa6d5ca1635adf033","tid":1074112,"uid":64720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit