,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T15:16:23.000Z","msg":"諗好耐都唔知想點"},{"pid":"9afbcfe3cfcbc5b6922ac0cb2a559c1f378d86c4","tid":1074112,"uid":174979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T20:39:58.000Z","msg":"bipolar disorder<br />\n長期喺重鬱期，可以食嘅藥都試哂咁濟，副作用好辛苦<br />\n特別食抗思覺失調藥嗰期，食到好高劑量都無效但副作用影響到日常工作唔到，總之好麻煩。<br />\n<br />\n之後轉用情緒穩定劑加抗抑鬱藥<br />\n家試緊最後一隻情緒穩定藥希望有效 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c7d83077d4ba230f5208a9dabf152ad5c076921","tid":1074112,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T21:11:31.000Z","msg":"停左藥仲辛苦<br />\n但食左藥 生理會出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d86be06d31b0476cd097ecc38c54da8852f39cb6","tid":1074112,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T21:11:49.000Z","msg":"好難揀 好辛苦呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a95f0898a12c271f560ef5c269f528cc7333cf6a","tid":1074112,"uid":229215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T11:55:29.000Z","msg":"食過，但有副作用同覺得繼續食既話就一世斷唔到尾<br />\n停藥嗰排係辛苦，情緒比平時更低落<br />\n雖然知自己一世都冇可能完全好得返，但覺得停咗藥個狀態係比較好"},{"pid":"25b5ee199e46d7275d93122c8d432a26c00bb954","tid":1074112,"uid":125903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"baa4f83a0698d49c0d5863f428f9dfb54533b4dd","tid":1074112,"uid":12219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e52ebe8f79f71df1d9dd615e6da49bc74befb39b","tid":1074112,"uid":125903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3651d96aba9a3376e8f8a40e7f99b94c3386f0c0","tid":1074112,"uid":12219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T15:50:30.000