rmal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4502c0decdde3c016f25377248e435d063604b28","tid":1074112,"uid":125903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c3d78f9cfe6f5aa7cd38a287a9749610af38750","tid":1074112,"uid":44098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T13:40:24.000Z","msg":"十二年前讀書時確診有depression<br />\n要即時食藥<br />\n嗰時好嚴重 又甩頭髮又盛<br />\n最後睇中醫好番<br />\n<br />\n之後斷斷續續都有復發<br />\n前幾年睇咗個心理學家<br />\n佢同我做咗個超長嘅test<br />\n佢話depression分好多種<br />\n我算係遺傳嗰種，好難斷尾<br />\n佢要求我唔好停西藥<br />\n但對我太多副作用<br />\n令到我記憶力集中力變差<br />\n所以我無食西藥<br />\n到而家為止都係睇緊中醫調理<br />\nso far唔錯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T13:58:40.000Z","msg":"絲打睇中醫有效果就ok啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔敢停西藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a704b7d213e3dd4daa133df36932d857ce1a0dc","tid":1074112,"uid":125903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a23ac1f6e3fe5087e74bd331ac2bfd52eae82e1b","tid":1074112,"uid":156854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T14:44:37.000Z","msg":"我都食緊<br />\n隻藥比較新<br />\n副作用較少<br />\n但工作要壓力大<br />\n一停就死<br />\n<br />\n但食住都穩定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比起以前好番好多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T13:59:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc302325b45b0a1efbefb250e1fe09cda1dc5975","tid":1074112,"uid":125903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ae8c5657183575b1e72658297b66b44ed8e82e2","tid":1074112,"uid":229215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91961ceb395be62c95913438c87deae04a4a08e0","tid":1074112,"uid":125903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a95f0898a12c271f560ef5c269f528cc7333cf6a","tid":1074112,"uid":229215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T11:55:29.000Z","msg":"食過，但有副作用同覺得繼續食既話就一世斷唔到尾<br />\n停藥嗰排係辛苦，情緒比平時更低落<br />\n雖然知自己一世都冇可能完全好得返，但覺得停咗藥個狀態係比較好"},"citedBy":1